OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775718328
OL,3,CNI schools continue to deal with
OL,4,Cfallout from cyber attack
OL,6,FSchools across Northern Ireland are
OL,7,Fcontinuing to deal with the fall-out
OL,8,Ffrom a cyber attack on their IT system.
OL,10,FThe Education Authority has been
OL,11,Fleading the response since Friday, and
OL,12,Fon Tuesday said that so far there's no
OL,13,Fevidence that data has been taken or
OL,14,Fcorrupted.
OL,16,FA statement said a full investigation
OL,17,Fis being undertaken and "intensive
OL,18,Fwork is ongoing to get C2k fully back
OL,19,Fto normal, as quickly and securely as
OL,20,Fpossible".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
