OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775718328
OL,3,CNI schools continue to deal with
OL,4,Cfallout from cyber attack
OL,6,FKaty Feeny, Principal of Banbridge
OL,7,FHigh School, is one of hundreds of
OL,8,Fschool leaders now working to get
OL,9,Fstudents and staff back online.
OL,11,FShe said: "Lots of our students were
OL,12,Fhoping to use this time to be able to
OL,13,Fconcentrate on revision and things
OL,14,Flike controlled assessments so it's
OL,15,Fbeen challenging in that we as a
OL,16,Fschool don't want to disadvantage any
OL,17,Fof the students.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775718328
OL,3,CNI schools continue to deal with
OL,4,Cfallout from cyber attack
OL,6,F"We've been working hard to manage
OL,7,Fpassword resets so they can access
OL,8,Fthings like Google Classroom and their
OL,9,FOneDrive so they can obviously
OL,10,Fprioritise their revision in such a
OL,11,Fcrucial period considering we've got
OL,12,Fexternal exams soon."
OL,14,FOn Friday the Education Authority
OL,15,Fconfirmed the C2K school system had
OL,16,Fbeen targeted. It described a full
OL,17,Fpassword reset - for emails and system
OL,18,Faccess - as critical.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
