OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775718328
OL,3,CNI schools continue to deal with
OL,4,Cfallout from cyber attack
OL,6,FPost primary schools were prioritised
OL,7,F- given examinations and revision. The
OL,8,FEA says work has since continued
OL,9,Faround the clock to restore services.
OL,11,FThe Education Authority said more than
OL,12,F300 schools were represented at an
OL,13,FInformation Webinar on Tuesday on the
OL,14,Fsteps required for pupils and staff to
OL,15,Freestablish their C2k accounts.
OL,17,FIt said a further 450 schools have
OL,18,Frequested recordings of the Webinar.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
