OL,3,CNI schools continue to deal with
OL,4,Cfallout from cyber attack
OL,6,FA statement added: "Any schools
OL,7,Fseeking further information and
OL,8,Fsupport on reestablishing their C2k
OL,9,Faccounts are asked to contact our
OL,10,FService Desk on 0800 0931 541 as soon
OL,11,Fas possible. The Service Desk will
OL,12,Fremain open 8am to 5pm throughout for
OL,13,Fthe remainder of this week and through
OL,14,Fthe incoming weekend."
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
